query:
WITH locked_tabular AS (
            SELECT tabular_id, protected
            FROM tabular
            WHERE tabular_id = $1
            FOR UPDATE
        )
        UPDATE tabular
        SET deleted_at = $2
        FROM locked_tabular lt
        WHERE tabular.tabular_id = lt.tabular_id
        RETURNING tabular.tabular_id, lt.protected as "protected!"
